                    d="M10.5 9.5C8.29086 9.5 6.5 11.2909 6.5 13.5V34.5C6.5 36.7091 8.29086 38.5 10.5 38.5H37.5C39.7091 38.5 41.5 36.7091 41.5 34.5V13.5C41.5 11.2909 39.7091 9.5 37.5 9.5H10.5Z"
